{"tid":1834811,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我依家好驚啲中國人會衝嚟緊醫病","createTime":"2020-01-22T14:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T15:27:03.000Z","uid":245523,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb5a271624801369ff9aea460b43e433d423f13","tid":1834811,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"今晚幾單衝咗去北京上海呢啲醫療系統較發達嘅大城市<br />\n一個小朋友中招 父母由武漢（好似）衝咗去上海兒科醫院 搞到人地要封院<br />\n南方嘅大陸人就會衝嚟澳門香港 平時點踩香港都好 去到生死關頭就會好誠實 <br />\n如果唔封關 香港醫院如果岀於人道主義精神收咗第一個嘅話 就會一車車病人湧落嚟 增加我地前線醫護工作量同危險性 本身已經爆煲嘅醫療系統會不勝負荷<br />\n希望唔好畀我估中"},{"pid":"bc27d10b715b4cc60232ce1f80dc709318fe2c82","tid":1834811,"uid":270791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"其實支那人係一定會衝落黎香港<br />\n邊個唔戴口罩染上左只可以講抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c34bdb5e86e20dafdc7e2981cf27e3949fe60b","tid":1834811,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc27d10b715b4cc60232ce1f80dc709318fe2c82","tid":1834811,"uid":270791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"其實支那人係一定會衝落黎香港<br />\n邊個唔戴口罩染上左只可以講抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:50:02.000Z","msg":"唔係自己一個有冇事咁簡單 我擔心本地醫療體系多啲 又唔係得肺炎一個病咁簡單<br />\n真係要中 你保護得好都係會中 如果醫療資源充足 康復都易啲 但係太多病人 跟唔嚟 醫護做餐死又易中招 亦都會令到更多人被傳染"},{"pid":"5d8fbd60f72ba0b8c3c57f9d2c4322f5dfd22cb4","tid":1834811,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"驚都無用因為一定會發生"},{"pid":"2e5adefcf4cf6ee6b29c201dea68516cba8610ae","tid":1834811,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎香港站既沙盤推演<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1834829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1834829</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩先開，點睇？"},{"pid":"2b905dd6f6d05f544718ff8d7c550d92223363fb","tid":1834811,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e5adefcf4cf6ee6b29c201dea68516cba8610ae","tid":1834811,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎香港站既沙盤推演<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1834829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1834829</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩先開，點睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"疫苗中硬<br />\n沙士到依家都未研發到疫苗 弱智支那仔仲話中國已經研發好不過冇推出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3437b84ead73a65c30dfbbc91c914c812b4fd1","tid":1834811,"uid":245523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/942fffu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F942fffu.png&h=bd206786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嚟了 樓主屋企人因為武漢醫療爆煲一直確唔到診 有人建議佢即刻走去第度醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa0bbf14e09aedf100d8325bb25b0c9ef35eba8","tid":1834811,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc27d10b715b4cc60232ce1f80dc709318fe2c82","tid":1834811,"uid":270791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"其實支那人係一定會衝落黎香港<br />\n邊個唔戴口罩染上左只可以講抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"其實2003年沙士根本就係咁"}]}